    "name": "RoseCloud Auth and User Flows",
    "description": "Login, logout, current user, user query, tenant switching, and token revocation flows for RoseCloud. Run the requests top to bottom the first time so token/session variables can be populated. The 租户 (tenant) folder logs in with 会话A, lists switchable tenants, switches to one of them, and verifies the new token's tenant claim actually changed.",
